snippet.title: Golf by the way - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A fast-paced real-time mini-golf party game with no stroke count! Play as an actual golfer in real-time and go SMACK your friends’ golf ball or even your friends themselves.

Wishlist now on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2550840/Golf_by_the_way/

Follow us on our social media and stay tune for more info!
